26|108| be, then, conscious of God, and pay heed unto me!
26|109| ‚ÄúAnd no reward whatever do I ask of you for it: my reward rests with none but the Sustainer of all the worlds.
26|110| Hence, remain conscious of God, and pay heed unto me!‚Äù
